description: Provides exposure to real estate securities focused on income derived from real estate investments and structured in a similar way as real estate investment trust (REITs).Pursues the benefits associated with indexing (diversification, low turnover, transparency of exposures), but with the ability to add value by making investment decisions using information in current prices. Efficient portfolio management and trading process that is designed to enhance returns while seeking to reduce unnecessary risks and costs for investors. Built to fit seamlessly into an investor's asset allocation.
name: Avantis Real Estate ETF
